{{#> base subject="KYC Application — Action Required"}}
  {{#*inline "body"}}
    <h2>KYC Application — Action Required</h2>
    <p>Dear <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>,</p>
    <p>We have reviewed your KYC application and unfortunately are unable to approve it at this time. Please review the details below and resubmit the required documentation.</p>

    <div class="danger-banner">
      <strong>⚠ Reason for rejection:</strong><br />
      {{reason}}
    </div>

    <p><strong>What to do next:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Review the rejection reason above carefully.</li>
      <li>Gather the correct or updated documentation.</li>
      <li>Log in to the AOP Portal and resubmit your KYC application.</li>
    </ol>

    <p>If you believe this decision is incorrect or need assistance, please contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>

    <hr class="divider" />
    <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;">Your account access is restricted until KYC is approved. Pending transactions are paused.</p>
  {{/inline}}
{{/base}}
